'''第60届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[1987年电影|1987年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]1988年4月11日下午18点（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上21点）在美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的神殿礼堂举行，共计颁发了22座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由小塞缪尔·戈尔德温担任[[制片人|制片人]]，马蒂·帕赛塔导演<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Van Gelder | first1 = Lawrence | title = At the Movies | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1987/10/30/movies/at-the-movies.html | accessdate = 2015-12-24 | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | date = 1987-10-27 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222232642/http://www.nytimes.com/1987/10/30/movies/at-the-movies.html | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last1 = Caulfield | first1 = Deborah | title = TV & Video | archivedate = 2015-06-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620185619/http://articles.latimes.com/1987-12-07/entertainment/ca-18140_1_tv-director | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1987-12-07/entertainment/ca-18140_1_tv-director | accessdate = 2015-12-24 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1987-12-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，男演员切维·切斯连续第二年担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Gilatto | first1 = Tom | title = Oscar Wild | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 1988-01-27}}</ref>。两周前的3月27日，[[雪莉·琼斯|雪莉·琼斯]]在加利福尼亚州[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[比弗利希尔顿酒店|比弗利希尔顿酒店]]主持颁发[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | publisher = AMPAS | archivedate = 2014-07-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140707000407/http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | title = Past Scientific & Technical Awards Ceremonies | accessdate = 2014-09-09 | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences}}</ref>。

《[[末代皇帝_(电影)|末代皇帝]]》赢得[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片奖]]，并为[[贝纳尔多·贝托鲁奇|贝纳尔多·贝托鲁奇]]拿下[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Harmetz | first1 = Aljean | title = 'The Last Emperor' Wins 9 Oscars And Is Named Best Film of 1987 | accessdate = 2015-12-25 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1988-04-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117055525/http://www.nytimes.com/1988/04/12/movies/the-last-emperor-wins-9-oscars-and-is-named-best-film-of-1987.html | publisher= Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | archivedate = 2015-11-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1988/04/12/movies/the-last-emperor-wins-9-oscars-and-is-named-best-film-of-1987.html}}</ref>。[[雪儿|雪儿]]和[[奥林匹亚·杜卡基斯|奥林匹亚·杜卡基斯]]分别因出演《[[月色撩人|月色撩人]]》获[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|女主角]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角奖]]。[[迈克尔·道格拉斯|迈克尔·道格拉斯]]因《[[华尔街_(1987年电影)|华尔街]]》获[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角奖]]，[[肖恩·康纳利|肖恩·康纳利]]凭《[[铁面无私|铁面无私]]》拿下[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117015002/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/news/mn-783_1_picture-winner | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/news/mn-783_1_picture-winner | title = 'Last Emperor' Reigns Over Oscar Ceremonies : Best Picture Winner Adds Eight Other Awards; Cher and Douglas Take Top Prizes for Acting | newspaper = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-12 | accessdate = 2015-12-25 | archivedate = 2015-11-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。颁奖典礼的电视直播在美国平均吸引了约4,220万观众收看。

== 获奖和提名 ==
[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]1988年2月16日早上5点38分（[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]13点38分），[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]主席[[罗伯特·怀斯|罗伯特·怀斯]]和女演员[[雪莉·麦克雷恩|雪莉·麦克雷恩]]一起在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布第60届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|712}}。《[[末代皇帝_(电影)|末代皇帝]]》以9项提名领跑，《[[收播新闻|收播新闻]]》以7项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | title = 'Emperor' Leads Topsy-Turvy Oscar Race : American Directors Are Shut Out for the First Time in Academy History | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-02-18/entertainment/ca-43482_1_emperor-leads-topsy-turvy-oscar-race | accessdate = 2015-12-26 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222120316/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-02-18/entertainment/ca-43482_1_emperor-leads-topsy-turvy-oscar-race | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Ryan | first = Desmond | title = The Oscar Nominees "The Last Emperor" And "Broadcast News" Lead The Field | accessdate = 2015-12-25 | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | url = http://articles.philly.com/1988-02-18/news/26240453_1_nominations-oscars-fatal-attraction | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | date = 1988-02-18 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222111049/http://articles.philly.com/1988-02-18/news/26240453_1_nominations-oscars-fatal-attraction}}</ref>。

获奖名单在1988年4月11日举行的颁奖典礼上公布。《末代皇帝》成为继1958年的《[[金粉世界|金粉世界]]》以来首部9项提名全部获奖的电影<ref>{{cite news | title = Some achievement, but not a record | work = The Vancouver Sun | publisher = Gordon Fisher | date = 1988-04-16 | page = D1}}</ref>。同时5位获导演奖提名的电影人都不是在美国出生，这还是历史上首次出现这种情况<ref>{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | title = No Oscars for U.S. Directors : Foreigners Win All Nominations; 9 for 'Last Emperor' | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-02-17/news/mn-29431_1_broadcast-news | accessdate = 2015-12-26 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151123132810/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-02-17/news/mn-29431_1_broadcast-news | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-11-23}}</ref>。获男主角奖的[[迈克尔·道格拉斯|迈克尔·道格拉斯]]曾因《[[飞越疯人院|飞越疯人院]]》夺得最佳影片奖，成为历史上第2位先后赢得表演和制片类奖项的电影人{{ref label|Douglas|A|}}<ref name="BEDO">{{cite news | last = Crook | first = John | title = Like Father, Like Son at the Golden Globes | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151123142037/http://articles.latimes.com/2004/jan/25/news/tv-coverstory25 | publisher = Austin Beutner | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2004/jan/25/news/tv-coverstory25 | accessdate = 2015-12-26 | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 2004-01-25}}</ref>。

