== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Chevy_Chase_(1990).jpg|thumb]]
1987年10月，美国电影艺术与科学学院决定聘请小塞缪尔·戈德温（{{lang|en|Samuel Goldwyn, Jr.}}）连续第2次为奥斯卡颁奖典礼操刀<ref>{{cite news | last = Lawrence | first = Van Gelder | title = At the Movies | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222211728/http://www.nytimes.com/1987/10/30/movies/at-the-movies.html?pagewanted=all | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1987/10/30/movies/at-the-movies.html?pagewanted=all | accessdate = 2015-12-25 | newspaper = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | date = 1987-10-30 | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>。过了3个月，戈德温宣布请男演员兼笑匠[[切維·切斯|切維·切斯]]担任晚会主持<ref>{{cite news | last = Schnurmacher | first = Thomas | title = SPAC, SPCA ask VIPs to RSVP ASAP | work = Montreal Gazette | publisher = Postmedia Network | date = 1988-01-18 | page = C9}}</ref>。此外，电影艺术和科学学院还决定从本届开始将颁奖典礼迁至神殿礼堂举行，此前的近20届颁奖典礼都是在[[多萝茜·钱德勒大厅|多萝茜·钱德勒大厅]]举办，与之相比，神殿礼堂更加宽阔，可以容纳更多宾客，颁奖典礼也能有更充裕的时间排练<ref>{{cite news | last = Culhane | first = John | title = With Help From Friends, Oscar's a Wit and Raconteur | newspaper = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | date = 1988-04-10 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1988/04/10/movies/with-help-from-friends-oscar-s-a-wit-and-raconteur.html | accessdate = 2015-12-25 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222114058/http://www.nytimes.com/1988/04/10/movies/with-help-from-friends-oscar-s-a-wit-and-raconteur.html}}</ref>。这也是1948年的[[第20届奥斯卡金像奖|第20届典礼]]后颁奖晚会首度回归神殿礼堂<ref>{{cite news | last = Voland | first = John | title = Oscar's Life Complicated by Writers' Strike, New Setting | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222103750/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-08/entertainment/ca-1014_1_guild-strike-rules/2 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-08/entertainment/ca-1014_1_guild-strike-rules/2 | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-08 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。戈德温和导演马蒂·帕塞塔（{{lang|en|Marty Pasetta}}）原计划把曾参演过之前59部奥斯卡最佳影片奖获奖电影的演员当年走过红地毯的镜头经剪辑后在颁奖典礼上播放，但由于出席晚会的部分来宾因交通问题导致到达现场的时间较迟，剪辑片段因此没有播映<ref>{{Cite book | last = Osborne | first = Robert | title = 80 Years of the Oscar: The Complete History of the Academy Awards | url = https://archive.org/details/80yearsofoscarof0000osbo | year = 2008 | isbn = 0-7892-0992-6 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Abbeville Publishing Group | page = [https://archive.org/details/80yearsofoscarof0000osbo/page/287 287]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Caulfield | first = Deborah | title = First Off... | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-13/entertainment/ca-745_1_traffic-jam | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-11 | archivedate = 2015-12-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222095449/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-13/entertainment/ca-745_1_traffic-jam}}</ref>。

1988年3月7日，[[1988年美国编剧协会大罢工|1988年美国编剧协会大罢工]]爆发，到一个多月后颁奖典礼开幕时仍未结束，对晚会的电视直播及周边构成影响。[[美国编剧协会|美国编剧协会]]不同意编剧为颁奖典礼编写台词，但作为晚会的3名首席编剧，[[恩斯特·莱赫曼|恩斯特·莱赫曼]]（{{lang|en|Ernest Lehman}}）、[[梅尔韦尔·沙维尔森|梅尔韦尔·沙维尔森]]（{{lang|en|Melville Shavelson}}）和[[杰克·罗斯|杰克·罗斯]]（{{lang|en|Jack Rose}}）还是准备好了超过一半的素材。<ref name="Strike Experience">{{cite news | last = Killday | title = Oscar has experience with strike-related uncertainty | work = The Hollywood Reporter | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2008-02-08 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-has-experience-strike-related-104329 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151125065308/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-has-experience-strike-related-104329 | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | archivedate = 2015-11-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。为了弥补剧本的缺失部分，戈德温请来包括约翰·坎迪（{{lang|en|John Candy}}）、[[比利·克里斯托|比利·克里斯托]]、[[艾迪·墨菲|艾迪·墨菲]]和[[罗宾·威廉姆斯|罗宾·威廉姆斯]]在内的多位笑匠随兴发挥<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|716}}<ref>{{cite news | last = Spillman | first = Susan | title = Hope and glory at the Oscars | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 1988-04-11 | page = 4D}}</ref>。多位出席颁奖典礼的艺人在晚会期间表态支持编剧，例如肖恩·康纳利就在上台接受男配角奖致辞时称：“如果这座奖可以伴随一个愿望，那我的愿望就是编剧罢工可以结束<ref>{{cite news | last = Voland | first = John | title = This Year, Most of the Thanks Go to Writers | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/entertainment/ca-969_1_writers | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-12 | archivedate = 2015-11-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151123135136/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/entertainment/ca-969_1_writers}}</ref>。”

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截至2月16日提名公布时，全部5部获最佳影片奖提名的电影在美国的[[票房|票房]]总收入为2亿2151万4287美元，平均每部4430万2857美元<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars">{{cite news | title = 1989 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1987&p=.htm | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905110206/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1987&p=.htm | publisher = Box Office Mojo (Amazon.com) | archivedate = 2015-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。其中《致命诱惑》以1亿4229万5229美元位居榜首，之后分别是收入3671万2098美元的《收播新闻》、进账2536万9070美元的《月色撩人》、收入1191万2886美元的末代皇帝和进账522万5004美元的《希望与荣耀》<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars" />。

在1987年[[美国电影|美国电影]]票房50强中，有17部电影获得共计39项提名。其中《致命诱惑》（亚军）、《铁面无私》（第4名）、《早安越南》（第10名）、《谋害老妈》（第14名）、《全金属外壳》（第21名）、《收播新闻》（第26名）、《华尔街》（第30名）和《月色撩人》（第39名）所获提名包含最佳影片、导演或编剧、表演类奖项。另外9部获提名的电影分别是《比佛利山超级警探2》（冠军）、《致命武器》（第7名）、《东镇女巫》（第8名）、《霹雳舞》（第9名）、《铁血战士》（第11名）、《机械战警》（第15名）、《神气活现》（第23名）、《公主新娘》（第38名）和《惊异大奇航》（第45名）<ref>{{cite news | title = 1987 Box Office Grosses (as of February 15, 1988) | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | publisher = Box Office Mojo (Amazon.com) | archivedate = 2014-07-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719002751/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1988-02-15&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1987&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1988-02-15&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1987&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
本次颁奖典礼所获评价不佳，大部分媒体看法倾向负面。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》电视评论员霍华德·罗森伯格（{{lang|en|Howard Rosenberg}}）评论称：“美国广播公司在周一晚直播的奥斯卡颁奖典礼就像电视颁奖节目中的[[麥可·杜卡基斯|麥可·杜卡基斯]]和[[乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什|乔治·布什]]：沉重、单调而且令人郁闷。你总希望他们会把[[马力欧·库默|马力欧·库默]]送出来。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Rosenberg | first = Howard | title = A Night With All the Excitement of an Envelope Opening | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-12 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/entertainment/ca-964_1_envelope-opening | accessdate = 2015-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151123131657/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/entertainment/ca-964_1_envelope-opening | archivedate = 2015-11-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）批评晚会毫无亮眼，即便考虑到往年遗留下来的低标准，本届颁奖典礼也显得异常低迷<ref>{{cite news | last = Shales | first = Tom | title = A Tortured New Look In Hollywood Horror | work = The Washington Post | publisher = The Washington Post Company | date = 1988-04-12}}</ref>。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》专栏作家马特·罗什（{{lang|en|Matt Roush}}）批评主持人切斯令现场一度又一度陷入冷场，试图带动气氛的即兴表演也少有成效。他还觉得《末代皇帝》赢得大部分奖项导致现场氛围更显沉闷而虎头蛇尾。<ref>{{cite news | last = Roush | first = Matt | title = A show short on surpises | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 1988-04-12}}</ref>

=== 收视率和奖项 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有约4220万观众收看，与[[第59届奥斯卡金像奖|前一年]]相比提高了13%<ref>{{cite news | last = Johnson | first = Greg | title = Call It the Glamour Bowl | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117032348/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/18/business/fi-18458/2 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/18/business/fi-18458/2 | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1999-03-18 | archivedate = 2015-11-17}}</ref>，而所有曾观看部分时段节目的观众总数则估计有7000万<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscars Push ABC to Win Ratings Race | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1990-04-03 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1990-04-03/entertainment/ca-864_1_ratings-race | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222140627/http://articles.latimes.com/1990-04-03/entertainment/ca-864_1_ratings-race | work = Los Angeles Times | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>。从尼尔森收视率调查的数据看，节目的表现好过前一年，吸引了29.2%的家庭观看，收视率超过49%<ref>{{cite news | title = ABC gets an Oscar boost | work = USA Today | page = 3D | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 1990-04-04}}</ref>。

1988年7月，颁奖典礼获第40届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]4项提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Nominations for Prime-Time Emmys | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-07-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222081230/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-07-29/entertainment/ca-8047_1_great-performances | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-07-29/entertainment/ca-8047_1_great-performances | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Primetime Emmy Award database | publisher = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences (ATAS) | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/60th-annual-academy-awards | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222142646/http://www.emmys.com/shows/60th-annual-academy-awards | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>，并在同年8月为小塞缪尔·戈德温赢得杰出综艺音乐节目奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Margulies | first = Lee | title = Cable Gets Prime-Time Emmys | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-25/entertainment/ca-1277_1_cable-program | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222134641/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-25/entertainment/ca-1277_1_cable-program | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

